headline.print_headline: Putin, in Call With Hollande, Urges Halt to 'Bloodshed' in Ukraine
headline.main: Putin, in Call With Hollande, Urges Halt to 'Bloodshed' in Ukraine

lead_paragraph: Russian President Vladimir Putin, in a telephone call with his French counterpart Francois Hollande on Friday, urged a halt to bloodshed in Ukraine and the start of talks between Kiev and eastern separatists.
